<p><i><b>The Corporation</b></i> is a 2003 <a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada">Canadian</a> <a href="/wiki/Documentary_film" title="Documentary film">documentary film</a> critical of the modern-day <a href="/wiki/Corporation" title="Corporation">corporation</a>, considering it as a class of <a href="/wiki/Person" title="Person">person</a> and evaluating its behaviour towards society and the world at large as a psychologist might evaluate an ordinary person. This is explored through specific examples.</p>
