<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Lucy_Hughes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Lucy Hughes (page does not exist)">Lucy Hughes</a>, vice president, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Initiative_Media&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Initiative Media (page does not exist)">Initiative Media</a></li>
