<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Robert_Keyes_(CEO)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Robert Keyes (CEO) (page does not exist)">Robert Keyes</a>, president and CEO, Canadian Council for International Business</li>
