<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chris_Komisarjevsky&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Chris Komisarjevsky (page does not exist)">Chris Komisarjevsky</a>, CEO, <a href="/w/index.php?title=Burson_Marsteller_Worldwide&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Burson Marsteller Worldwide (page does not exist)">Burson Marsteller Worldwide</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dr._Susan_Linn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Dr. Susan Linn (page does not exist)">Dr. Susan Linn</a>, Prof. of Psychiatry, Baker Children’s Center, Harvard</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Robert_Monks" title="Robert Monks" class="mw-redirect">Robert Monks</a>, corporate governance adviser and shareholder activist</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sir_Mark_Moody-Stuart&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Sir Mark Moody-Stuart (page does not exist)">Sir Mark Moody-Stuart</a>, former chairman, <a href="/wiki/Royal_Dutch_Shell" title="Royal Dutch Shell">Royal Dutch Shell</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Michael_Moore" title="Michael Moore">Michael Moore</a>, author, filmmaker</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Oscar_Olivera" title="Oscar Olivera">Oscar Olivera</a>, leader, Coalition in Defense of Water and Life</li>
